latestPosts.caption:
Avni and Raghav — a living symphony of this of this song, ye moh moh ke dhaage: threads of attraction, threads of love. 🧡

As a makeup artist, when we decide to spend hours and hours together, we don’t just do makeup. We witness your story, we witness your love and then, we hope to make you a bride that justifies the person you are, the bond that you have. 

The love we witnessed was pure, was golden, was bright. There was freshness of gajra and the warmth of sunshine: reflected exactly in her most special, bridal look. ✨
